Package: accountingToolsR
Type: Package
Title: Accounting and Financial Reporting Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Elizabeth", "Stanny", , "stanny@sonoma.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7580-9427"))
Description: Provides a suite of tools for bookkeeping, financial reporting, 
    and modeling for private companies. This package includes functions for 
    recording transactions, defining and managing the chart of accounts, 
    generating financial statements, making adjusting and closing entries, 
    and visualizing financial performance. Built on the tidyverse ecosystem 
    for efficient data manipulation and analysis.
